General.Name: Sedlmayr Grund und Immobilien AG
General.Description: Sedlmayr Grund und Immobilien AG acquires, develops, and manages real estate properties in Germany. The company owns and rents commercial spaces, apartments, restaurants, and residential and commercial buildings, as well as related investments and maintenance services. The company was formerly known as Sedlmayr Grund und Immobilien KGaA and changed its name to Sedlmayr Grund und Immobilien AG in October 2018. Sedlmayr Grund und Immobilien AG was founded in 1397 and is headquartered in Munich, Germany. Sedlmayr Grund und Immobilien AG is a subsidiary of Sedlmayr Treuhandgesellschaft mbH.
